This paper deals with generating adversarial examples for image classifiers, which is a problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses optimization methods and query efficiency, which are topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of patches, which is a common technique in computer graphics and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper deals with security and attacks, which is a topic in cryptography (cs.CR).
